    <CEEvent>
        <Name>TB_companion_fighting_m</Name>
        <Text>{=TBRandomEventsCompanion005}You hear yelling and cheering, and when you go to investigate you discover{COMPANION_NAME_1} seems to have gotten into a fight with one of your troops. They're punching each other bloody as the rest of your men cheer them on and start betting on the outcome. The man he's fighting looks like a pretty burly fighter... Hopefully he doesn't get badly hurt.</Text>
